I’ve always been the “hydration is going to solve all my problems” girl 🌸🧖🏼‍♀️

And the most important step in my morning routine has always been a moisturiser that keeps my skin hydrated all day, so I don’t have to keep reapplying. This one from @komyo.wellness does all the work for my skin, minus the greasiness.

Pro tip: Apply it while your skin is still slightly damp..it really helps lock in moisture so much better.
